    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong>《King’s Bounty: Crossworlds》包含完整的《King’s Bounty: Armored Princess》战役，以及两条额外的迷你战役：以角斗场首领战为核心的《Champion of the Arena》，以及在独特竞技场中、使用随机盟友与敌人的战术对战模式《Defender of the Crown》。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63910/extras/740d8995b1ed100b2d71d749bdc39931.poster.avif?t=1770997210\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63910/extras/740d8995b1ed100b2d71d749bdc39931.webm?t=1770997210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63910/extras/740d8995b1ed100b2d71d749bdc39931.mp4?t=1770997210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Armored Princess》战役还包含其专属扩展内容《Orcs on the March》，通过新增数十个任务、生物、物品、能力和法术，大幅提升了游戏的深度与多样性。全新的装备套装和机制带来更多战略选择，鼓励玩家尝试不同的军队组合与玩法风格。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crossworlds 还内置了功能完整的世界编辑器，让你能够创建属于自己的地图、战役和战术挑战。设计自定义场景、测试战斗并与其他玩家分享你的作品，使游戏寿命远远超出内置战役的范围。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63910/extras/8f36cfc8542361cf78ab222c0ea3b6c4.poster.avif?t=1770997210\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63910/extras/8f36cfc8542361cf78ab222c0ea3b6c4.webm?t=1770997210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63910/extras/8f36cfc8542361cf78ab222c0ea3b6c4.mp4?t=1770997210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你是想完整体验《Armored Princess》战役，在专注的战术挑战中检验实力，还是打造属于自己的《King’s Bounty》冒险，《King’s Bounty: Crossworlds》都为喜爱深度、多样性与战略自由的玩家带来了内容极其丰富的大型战术体验。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63910/extras/5a5190f363faeab8582d53bfeb49ac68.poster.avif?t=1770997210\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63910/extras/5a5190f363faeab8582d53bfeb49ac68.webm?t=1770997210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63910/extras/5a5190f363faeab8582d53bfeb49ac68.mp4?t=1770997210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>包含完整《Armored Princess》战役的独立资料片。</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提供完整的《King’s Bounty: Armored Princess》体验，包括实时探索、深度回合制战术战斗、英雄成长、同伴系统以及不断进化的宠物巨龙。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>两条额外的独立迷你战役。</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Champion of the Arena》专注于紧张刺激的角斗场战斗与首领对决，而《Defender of the Crown》则在独特竞技场中提供使用随机盟友与敌人的战术场景。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>包含《Orcs on the March》扩展内容。</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Armored Princess》战役包含其专属扩展《Orcs on the March》，新增单位、法术和任务，大幅扩展原有游戏体验。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扩展的战术选项与成长系统。</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新的装备套装、技能和机制加深了军队构建与战斗策略，为战斗提供更多应对方式。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>以竞技场为核心的玩法模式。</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在没有长时间探索的情况下体验《King’s Bounty》的战斗，专为追求高密度战术挑战与更快节奏的玩家设计。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>功能完整的世界编辑器。</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创建你自己的地图、战役和战术场景，自定义战斗并与社区分享你的内容。</p>",
